OOC: Rdahl told me i could control the ship. If anyone has a problem with 
this post, please tell me.

:::Hun-Grr:::

::As their small ship drifts through space, Hun-Grr spots earth. He 
remembered back in the Great War when he and the other Terrorcons played 
large parts. He had learned on Cybertron that a war was raging on earth, so 
he and the other Terrorcons got this ship and decided to get into the war::
Hun-Grr: All Terrorcons report to Hun-grr.  We nearing Earth.
(Alright guys, you know what to do!)
